Eclipse MAT (memory analysis) is available as a standalone tool:
https://www.eclipse.org/mat/downloads.php

To install:
 * Download by following x86_64 links from https://www.eclipse.org/mat/downloads.php .
cp MemoryAnalyzer-1.9.0.20190605-linux.gtk.x86_64.zip ~/bin/install
cd ~/bin/install
unzip MemoryAnalyzer-1.9.0.20190605-linux.gtk.x86_64.zip

## I cannot get the below to work, so just download directly, as explained above.
